  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/d8a0c6cb91683dc5769ee84c68354e0b.avif?t=1767486001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras_big/d8a0c6cb91683dc5769ee84c68354e0b.avif?t=1767486001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hey!</strong> Is your wife driving you up the wall? Are the kids constantly misbehaving? Is your boss blowing up your phone? Do you just want to take a break and mow your lawn? Well, now you can! Try out <strong>A</strong> <strong>Game About Mowing Your Lawn Today!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes place in your small backyard. Your grass is waiting for you. Will you cut it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/4dfa7caf4c236eefd865d66c96e73e9a.poster.avif?t=1767486001\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/4dfa7caf4c236eefd865d66c96e73e9a.webm?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/4dfa7caf4c236eefd865d66c96e73e9a.mp4?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of danger-filled mowing action.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid land mines, rocks, and other traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 15 to 30 minute playthrough​.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/bf9184d0b6894e52c6832ce79e6b2666.poster.avif?t=1767486001\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/bf9184d0b6894e52c6832ce79e6b2666.webm?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/bf9184d0b6894e52c6832ce79e6b2666.mp4?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/3732934a264c158883db344fd156dd84.avif?t=1767486001\" width=367 height=267 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/d8a0c6cb91683dc5769ee84c68354e0b.avif?t=1767486001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras_big/d8a0c6cb91683dc5769ee84c68354e0b.avif?t=1767486001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hey!</strong> Is your wife driving you up the wall? Are the kids constantly misbehaving? Is your boss blowing up your phone? Do you just want to take a break and mow your lawn? Well, now you can! Try out <strong>A</strong> <strong>Game About Mowing Your Lawn Today!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes place in your small backyard. Your grass is waiting for you. Will you cut it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/4dfa7caf4c236eefd865d66c96e73e9a.poster.avif?t=1767486001\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/4dfa7caf4c236eefd865d66c96e73e9a.webm?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/4dfa7caf4c236eefd865d66c96e73e9a.mp4?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of danger-filled mowing action.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid land mines, rocks, and other traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 15 to 30 minute playthrough​.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/bf9184d0b6894e52c6832ce79e6b2666.poster.avif?t=1767486001\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/bf9184d0b6894e52c6832ce79e6b2666.webm?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/bf9184d0b6894e52c6832ce79e6b2666.mp4?t=1767486001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3553880/extras/3732934a264c158883db344fd156dd84.avif?t=1767486001\" width=367 height=267 /></span></p>",
